Currently, the office

204
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,120
has 10 first-rank maids,

205
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,200
20 second-rank maids,

206
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,320
and 30 third-rank maids.

207
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,150
So the monthly salary expenses are...

208
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,320
Fourty-one taels.

209
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,750
Zhong Yunxin.

210
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,630
What's wrong, Miss Xu?

211
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,790
My math can't be wrong.

212
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:11,790
Yunxin, you're so good at math.

213
00:11:11,870 --> 00:11:13,240
