due to my status.

215
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,550
If you keep saying that,

216
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:20,870
I'll really get angry.

217
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,440
As my friend, you can call me Xinglan.

218
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:25,000
Okay, Miss Xu.

219
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,470
Xinglan.

220
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:33,300
